{"tid":629532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友好有錢 好自卑","createTime":"2018-04-14T18:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T22:31:54.000Z","uid":128057,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7384f77c114a7524e5ad48398fc7456539d6019","tid":629532,"uid":128057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"圈子朋友個個都有錢到一個點<br />\n幾千萬到幾億都有<br />\n個個間屋都大到痴線<br />\n最close個個fd仲要再癲啲 未出黎做野已經有二千萬樓做畢業禮物<br />\n每次上到朋友屋企都好葡萄<br />\n心入面好不甘 好唔開心<br />\n點解可以大我咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲要租緊樓住炸..<br />\n雖然已經逼自己唔好諗咁負面<br />\n但係每次一上朋友屋企真係忍唔住心入面唉 好絕望<br />\n自己可能連人地小小都及唔上<br />\n根本差九條街<br />\n有陣時真係會諗學會股胎好重要<br />\n好想regame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以教我點正面啲處理呢個心情.."},{"pid":"465982ba1da07319c95c4fbdfa59918219f34f1f","tid":629532,"uid":44869,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"人生唔係只有金錢"},{"pid":"da295cda3cd7e63e07dcc786e037c80937f689ab","tid":629532,"uid":128057,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"465982ba1da07319c95c4fbdfa59918219f34f1f","tid":629532,"uid":44869,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"人生唔係只有金錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"以前都冇咁著重 慢慢長大就知錢好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830eb0795a0f26728301b8693ebff261cf65187a","tid":629532,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:23:25.000Z","msg":"叫佢介紹啲有錢女你識"},{"pid":"97dd4ddff34db56d14b459cf7a24e333403c910d","tid":629532,"uid":12039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:23:47.000Z","msg":"無錢就搵錢"},{"pid":"1960e16a8175f147a42937e3e445c86b4e7ad079","tid":629532,"uid":128057,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"830eb0795a0f26728301b8693ebff261cf65187a","tid":62953